<h1>FAQs</h1>

  <!-- Content -->
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>How can I purchase your products?</strong><br>
      You can purchase through our website.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Can I open the package before paying the courier?</strong><br>
      Unfortunately, you cannot. Couriers are not allowed to wait for try‑ons or return with opened packages.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Where can I find the size chart?</strong><br>
      The size chart is available in the product gallery on each product page on our website.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>How long does delivery take?</strong><br>
      Orders are delivered within 5–8 business days in Cairo, Giza, and Alexandria. Deliveries to other governorates take up to 9 business days.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Can I make my order arrive faster?</strong><br>
      Unfortunately, no. Orders are shipped according to the courier’s delivery schedule, and delivery times cannot be expedited.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Do you have a physical store?</strong><br>
      No, we operate exclusively online.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Do you allow exchanges/returns?</strong><br>
      Yes, but some items may not be eligible for returns or exchanges. Please review our return/exchange policy on the website before placing your order.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>How to request a refund, exchange, or cancel my order?</strong><br>
      Please send an email to: veekegy@gmail.com. Please note: Orders are confirmed one day after being placed. Once confirmed, cancellations are not allowed.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>How can I contact you?</strong><br>
      Reach out through DM, our Contact Us page, or email: veekegy@gmail.com.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>What happens if the courier cannot deliver my order?</strong><br>
      The courier will attempt delivery once. If the order is not received, it will be automatically canceled.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Can I order two sizes of the same item and pay for the one that fits?</strong><br>
      This is not allowed. Such orders are automatically canceled by our website system. This is against our policy, and couriers are not allowed to return opened packages.
    </li>
  </ol>
<style>
/* ---------- Header / Nav ---------- */
nav {
    background-color: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 15px 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
}

nav ul li {
    display: inline;
}

/* ---------- Page Title ---------- */
h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #222;
    margin: 30px 0 20px;
    font-size: 28px;
}

h2 {
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

h3 {
    color: #777;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

/* ---------- FAQ List ---------- */
ol {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px 25px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

ol li {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: left;
}

ol li strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #000;
}

/* ---------- Links and Emails ---------- */
ol li a {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: underline;
}

ol li a:hover {
    color: #555;
}

/* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    ol {
        max-width: 90%;
        padding: 15px 15px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 20px 0 15px;
    }

    ol li {
        font-size: 14px;
    }
}

/* ---------- Extra Small Screens ---------- */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
    ol {
        padding: 12px 12px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
    }

    ol li {
        font-size: 13px;
    }
}
</style>
